T    C*          @NNNM     DIV  @DAY      AAAAA  101
T    C           @NNNM     DIV  20        AAAAA  101
     C           AAAAA     ADD  0.9       BBBBB   90
     C           BBBBB     MULT @DAY1     @N1NM
     C           BBBBB     MULT @DAY2     @N2NM
